-- Chile Probe Finds Bachelet’s Father Died From Torture, Emol Says
-- B y   R a n d a l l   W o o d s
-- 2012-06-20T18:03:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-20/chile-probe-finds-bachelet-s-father-died-from-torture-emol-says.html
Alberto Bachelet, a former Chilean
 air force  general and father of former President Michelle Bachelet, died as a result of torture conducted while he was
imprisoned after the military coup of 1973, El Mercurio’s online
edition Emol.com  reported today , citing magistrate Mario
Carroza.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Randall Woods in Santiago at 
 rwoods13@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
